ccsgp_get_started
-----------------

install virtualenv if you haven't yet. With MacPorts:
$ sudo port install py27-virtualenv

then:
$ git clone gitlab:github/ccsgp_get_started.git --recursive
$ cd ccsgp_get_started/
$ virtualenv-2.7 env
$ ./pip install -r requirements.txt
$ ./python -m pyana -h
$ ./python -m pyana <subname>

symlink pyanaDir to somewhere else to get started on your own data.
